# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

~> **Deprecated:** This data source is deprecated and will be removed in a future release of the provider. Consider using dedicated clusters with the [`scylladbcloud_cluster`](../resources/cluster) resource instead.

Retrieves the connection bundle for a ScyllaDB Cloud serverless cluster. The connection bundle contains all the information needed to establish a secure connection to your serverless cluster, including certificates and connection endpoints.

